{"title":"C_STL","uid":"c7326b4c451f518385b418d9140aee06","slug":"C/C_STL","date":"2021-11-02T00:39:04.000Z","updated":"2022-06-25T02:49:45.867Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/C/C_STL.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/C_STL.jpeg","content":"<h1 id=\"vector\"><a href=\"#vector\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"vector\"></a>vector</h1><h2 id=\"基本函数实现\"><a href=\"#基本函数实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本函数实现\"></a>基本函数实现</h2><h3 id=\"1-构造函数\"><a href=\"#1-构造函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.构造函数\"></a>1.构造函数</h3><p><strong>vector()</strong> : 创建一个空vector<br><strong>vector(n, x)</strong> : 创建n个元素值均为t<br><strong>vector(begin,end)</strong> : 复制[begin,end)区间内另一个数组的元素到vector中</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-增加函数\"><a href=\"#2-增加函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.增加函数\"></a>2.增加函数</h3><p><strong>void push_back(x)</strong> ： 尾部增加元素X<br><strong>iterator insert(it, x)</strong> : 迭代器指向元素前增加x</p>\n<h3 id=\"3-删除函数\"><a href=\"#3-删除函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.删除函数\"></a>3.删除函数</h3><p><strong>iterator erase(it)</strong> : 删除向量中迭代器指向元素<br><strong>iterator erase(it1,it2)</strong> : 删除向量中[first,last)中元素<br><strong>void pop_back()</strong> : 删除向量中最后一个元素<br><strong>void clear()</strong> : 清空向量中所有元素</p>\n<h3 id=\"4-遍历函数\"><a href=\"#4-遍历函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.遍历函数\"></a>4.遍历函数</h3><p><strong>reference at(pos)</strong> : 返回pos位置元素引用<br><strong>reference front()&#x2F;back()</strong> : 返回首尾元素引用<br><strong>iterator begin()&#x2F;end()</strong> : 返回头指针、尾元素下一位置指针<br>reverse_iterator rbegin() : 反向迭代器，指向最后一个元素<br>reverse_iterator rend() : 反向迭代器，指向第一个元素之前的位置</p>\n<h3 id=\"5-判断函数\"><a href=\"#5-判断函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.判断函数\"></a>5.判断函数</h3><p><strong>bool empty()</strong> : 判断是否为空<br><strong>int size()</strong> : 返回元素个数</p>\n<h2 id=\"访问\"><a href=\"#访问\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"访问\"></a>访问</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">int a[] &#x3D; &#123;10, 20, 30, 40, 50&#125;;\nvector&lt;int&gt; v(a,a+5);\nfor(int i&#x3D;0;i&lt;5;i++)\n    cout&lt;&lt;v[i]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;\n\nvector&lt;int&gt;::iterator it;\nfor(it&#x3D;v.begin();it!&#x3D;v.end();it++)\n    cout&lt;&lt;*it&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"二维数组\"><a href=\"#二维数组\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二维数组\"></a>二维数组</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">int N&#x3D;5, M&#x3D;6; &#x2F;&#x2F;定义二维动态数组5行6列 \nvector&lt;vector&lt;int&gt; &gt; v(N, vector&lt;int&gt;(M));\n\nfor(int i&#x3D;0; i&lt; v.size(); i++)\n    for(int j&#x3D;0;j&lt;v[i].size();j++)\n        cout&lt;&lt;v[i][j]&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;;</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h1 id=\"list\"><a href=\"#list\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"list\"></a>list</h1><h2 id=\"常用操作函数\"><a href=\"#常用操作函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用操作函数\"></a>常用操作函数</h2><p>同vector，此外有</p>\n<p><strong>lst.assign(n, x)</strong> : 赋值n个x<br><strong>lst.merge(lst1)</strong> : lst1合并到lst<br><strong>lst.pop_front()&#x2F;push_front()</strong> : 在头部删&#x2F;添加元素<br><strong>lst.remove()</strong> : 从list删除元素<br>lst.remove_if() : 按指定条件删除元素<br><strong>lst.reverse()</strong> : 把list的元素倒转<br><strong>lst.sort()</strong> : 给list排序<br><strong>lst.splice(lst1)</strong> : lst1剪切到lst<br><strong>lst.swap()</strong> : 交换两个list<br><strong>lst.unique()</strong> : 删除list中相邻重复的元素</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"set\"><a href=\"#set\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"set\"></a>set</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>set 作用是自动去重并按升序排序，适合需去重但是却不方便开数组的情况</p>\n<p>set 中元素是唯一的，如果需要处理不唯一的情况，则需要使用 multiset</p>\n<p>unordered_set 可以用来处理只去重但不排序的需求，速度比 set 要快得多</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"函数\"><a href=\"#函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数\"></a>函数</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">st.insert(3);\nauto it&#x3D;st.find(3);\nst.erase(it);\nst.erase(3);\nst.size();\nst.clear();</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"自定义排序\"><a href=\"#自定义排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自定义排序\"></a>自定义排序</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">struct cmp &#123;\n\tbool operator() (const int&amp; lhs, const int&amp; rhs) const&#123;\n\t\treturn lhs &gt; rhs;\n\t&#125;\n&#125;;\nint main()&#123;\n\tint a[] &#x3D; &#123;10, 20, 30, 40, 50&#125;;\n\tset&lt;int, cmp&gt; s(a, a + 5);\n\tfor (auto it &#x3D; s.begin(); it !&#x3D; s.end(); it++)\n\t\tcout &lt;&lt; *it &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot;;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"map\"><a href=\"#map\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"map\"></a>map</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> map: 自动按Key升序排序（红黑树），增删查改O(logn)</p>\n<p> unorder_map: 哈希存储无序，增删查改O(1)</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a>定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">map&lt;string,int&gt; m;\nmap&lt;string,int&gt; m &#x3D; &#123;&#123;&quot;Jim&quot;,4&#125;,&#123;&quot;Tom&quot;,6&#125;&#125;;\nmap&lt;string,int&gt; m1(m);\nmap&lt;string,int&gt; m1(++m.begin(),m.end());</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"访问-1\"><a href=\"#访问-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"访问\"></a>访问</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">m.at(&quot;Tom&quot;);&#x2F;&#x2F;无则报错\nm[&quot;Tom&quot;];   &#x2F;&#x2F;无则自动添加，类似insert\nm.find(&quot;Tom&quot;) &#x2F;&#x2F;返回迭代器，否则m.end()\n\nfor (auto x: m) &#123;\n    cout&lt;&lt;x.first&lt;&lt;&quot; &quot;&lt;&lt;x.second&lt;&lt;endl;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"插入\"><a href=\"#插入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"插入\"></a>插入</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">m.insert(pair&lt;string,int&gt;(&quot;student&quot;,1));\nm1.insert(m.begin(),m.end());</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"删除\"><a href=\"#删除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除\"></a>删除</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">m.erase(m.find(&quot;Jim&quot;));&#x2F;&#x2F;迭代器删除，返回i下一个迭代器\nm.erase(&quot;Tom&quot;);\t&#x2F;&#x2F;key删除，返回删除元素数目\nm.clear();  &#x2F;&#x2F;清空</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"仅Map\"><a href=\"#仅Map\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"仅Map\"></a>仅Map</h2><p><strong>size_t  count(key)</strong> : 返回key出现的次数0&#x2F;1</p>\n<p><strong>lower_bound()</strong> : 返回键值&gt;&#x3D;给定元素的第一个位置</p>\n<p><strong>upper_bound()</strong> : 返回键值&gt;给定元素的第一个位置</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"priority-queue\"><a href=\"#priority-queue\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"priority_queue\"></a>priority_queue</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>维护前k大的序列用小顶堆，第k+1个时队首(最小)出队</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"定义-1\"><a href=\"#定义-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a>定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">priority_queue&lt;Type, Container, Functional&gt;;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;默认大顶堆,容器vector\npriority_queue&lt;int&gt; q;\n&#x2F;&#x2F;小顶堆\npriority_queue &lt;int,vector&lt;int&gt;,greater&lt;int&gt; &gt; q;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"函数-1\"><a href=\"#函数-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数\"></a>函数</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">top()\npop()\npush()\nempty()\nsize()</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"比较方式\"><a href=\"#比较方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"比较方式\"></a>比较方式</h2><p>1.重载运算符<code>&quot;&lt;&quot;</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">struct fruit &#123;\n\tstring name;\n\tint price;\n\tfriend bool operator &lt; (fruit f1,fruit f2)&#123;\n\t\treturn f1.peice &lt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;大顶堆 \n    \treturn f1.peice &gt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;小顶堆 \n\t&#125;\n&#125;;</code></pre>\n\n<p>2.仿函数</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">struct cmp&#123;\n\tbool operator()(fruit f1,fruit f2)&#123;\n\t\treturn f1.price &lt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;大顶堆\n\t\treturn f1.price &gt; f2.price; &#x2F;&#x2F;小顶堆\n\t&#125;\n&#125;;\npriority_queue&lt;fruit,vector&lt;fruit&gt;,cmp&gt; q;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"string\"><a href=\"#string\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"string\"></a>string</h1><h2 id=\"比较\"><a href=\"#比较\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"比较\"></a>比较</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">string s&#x3D;&quot;abc11&quot;,t&#x3D;&quot;bc11&quot;;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 运算符 &gt;、&lt;、&#x3D;&#x3D;、&gt;&#x3D;、&lt;&#x3D;、!&#x3D;\ns&lt;&#x3D;t  s&gt;t &#x2F;&#x2F;1 0\n&#x2F;&#x2F; compare  返回-1 0 1\ns.compare(t) &#x2F;&#x2F; -1,小于\ns.compare(1,4,t,0,2) &#x2F;&#x2F; 切片“bc1”和“bc”</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"切片\"><a href=\"#切片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"切片\"></a>切片</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">string s(&quot;12345&quot;);\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; substr(start,length)\ns.substr(1,4); &#x2F;&#x2F; 2345\n&#x2F;&#x2F; substring(start,end)\ns.substring(1,5)  &#x2F;&#x2F;TODO</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">map&lt;string,int&gt; dic &#x3D; &#123;\n    &#123;&quot;I&quot;, 1&#125;,&#123;&quot;IV&quot;,4&#125;,&#123;&quot;IX&quot;,9&#125;\n&#125;;\nstring s &#x3D; &quot;IVV&quot;;\nstring ss &#x3D; s.substring(0,2); &#x2F;&#x2F;&quot;IV&quot;\nint n &#x3D; dic[ss]; &#x2F;&#x2F; 4\nreverse(s.begin(),s.end());</code></pre>\n\n","feature":true,"text":"vector基本函数实现1.构造函数vector() : 创建一个空vectorvector(n, x) : 创建n个元素值均为tvector(begin,end) : 复制[begin,end)区间内另一个数组的元素到vector中 2.增加函数void push_back(x...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"C","slug":"C","count":3,"path":"api/categories/C.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"C","slug":"C","count":3,"path":"api/tags/C.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#vector\"><span class=\"toc-text\">vector</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基本函数实现</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.构造函数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.增加函数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.删除函数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.遍历函数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5.判断函数</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">